    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271090/extras/57243e1679100428c9b656cf276de172.poster.avif?t=1730038474\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271090/extras/57243e1679100428c9b656cf276de172.webm?t=1730038474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271090/extras/57243e1679100428c9b656cf276de172.mp4?t=1730038474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The game features a VHS-inspired visual style with a low-poly aesthetic reminiscent of PS1-era graphics. The environment is intentionally grainy and pixelated, with heavy use of lighting effects and CRT screen filters to evoke the feel of old analog video.<br><br>In this horror game, you play as a young woman returning from work. Running low on gas, you pull into a gas station, but there's no gas to be found. Something feels off, and a sense of unease creeps in as you realize you might not be alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271090/extras/a6d3d5d2e68d218e680fbac03668b2a7.poster.avif?t=1730038474\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271090/extras/a6d3d5d2e68d218e680fbac03668b2a7.webm?t=1730038474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271090/extras/a6d3d5d2e68d218e680fbac03668b2a7.mp4?t=1730038474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay quiet and use the environment in your favor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid the killer by hiding in lockers or in the vents.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look for supplies like meds and flashlight batteries.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the puzzles to advance in the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find places to save the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lock the doors if you don't want to get chopped.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you hear anything, don't stop running.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271090/extras/e574128124046318a55ec55d597ffd49.avif?t=1730038474\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271090/extras_big/e574128124046318a55ec55d597ffd49.avif?t=1730038474 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul>",
